                                h4.person-name Bruce Almighty
                                p.person-title Dreams feel real while we're in them.
                        .column.media-object.card-person.stack-for-small
                            .media-object-section
                                img.avatar.avatar--large.circle(src='/img/people-profiles/prof-tyler.jpg')
                            .media-object-section.main-section.align-self-middle
                                h4.person-name Bandobras "Bullroarer" Took
                                p.person-title I Can Stack.
                    .row
                        .columns.small-12
                            h3.section-article--header-group Wrap cards in a callout class for variations
                    .row.small-up-1.medium-up-2
                        .column
                            .callout
                                p.person-quote
                                    | I'm going to improvise. Listen, there's something you should know about me... about inception. An idea is like a virus, resilient, highly contagious. The smallest seed of an idea can grow. It can grow to define or destroy you.
                                .column.media-object.card-person.stack-for-small
                                    .media-object-section
                                        img.avatar.avatar--large.circle(src='/img/people-profiles/prof-madeleine.jpg')
